---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Dither from "../../components/Dither.tsx";
---

<BaseLayout title="Personal Website | Bryce Keeler">
  <section class="project-detail-page">
    <!-- Background -->
    <div class="hero-bg no-fade">
      <Dither
        client:load
        waveSpeed={0.05}
        waveFrequency={3}
        waveAmplitude={0.3}
        waveColor={[0.4, 0.4, 0.4]}
        colorNum={4}
        pixelSize={2}
        disableAnimation={false}
        enableMouseInteraction={true}
        mouseRadius={0.1}
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Top menu pill -->
    <nav class="top-menu">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/projects">Projects</a>
      <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
    </nav>

    <!-- Project content -->
    <div class="project-container">
      <a href="/projects" class="back-link">← Back to Projects</a>

      <h1 class="project-title">This Website!</h1>

      <div class="project-meta">
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span class="tech-tag">Astro</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">TypeScript</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">CSS</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">JavaScript</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Web Dev</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Git</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/BryceKeeler720/PersonalWebsite" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="external-link">
            View on GitHub →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-content">
        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Overview</h2>
          <p>
            A modern, performant personal portfolio website built with Astro and React. Features a custom WebGL
            dithered wave background, glass morphism UI elements, and a clean, minimal design aesthetic.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Design Philosophy</h2>
          <p>
            The design focuses on creating a memorable first impression while maintaining excellent performance
            and accessibility. The animated background provides visual interest without overwhelming the content,
            and the glass morphism navigation creates depth and hierarchy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Key Features</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>WebGL Dithered Waves:</strong> Custom shader-based background animation using React Three Fiber</li>
            <li><strong>Glass Morphism UI:</strong> Blurred, semi-transparent navigation with backdrop filters</li>
            <li><strong>Dark Theme:</strong> Consistent dark color palette with neon green accents</li>
            <li><strong>Responsive Design:</strong> Fully responsive across all device sizes</li>
            <li><strong>Performance Optimized:</strong> Static site generation with selective hydration</li>
            <li><strong>Blog System:</strong> MDX support for rich blog content</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Technical Stack</h2>
          <p><strong>Frontend Framework:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Astro 5.16.2 - Static site generator with partial hydration</li>
            <li>React 19 - For interactive components</li>
            <li>TypeScript - Type-safe development</li>
          </ul>

          <p><strong>Styling:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Scoped CSS with Astro</li>
            <li>Ubuntu font family from Google Fonts</li>
            <li>Custom animations and transitions</li>
          </ul>

          <p><strong>3D Graphics:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>React Three Fiber - React renderer for Three.js</li>
            <li>@react-three/postprocessing - Post-processing effects</li>
            <li>Custom GLSL shaders for wave patterns</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>The Dithered Wave Background</h2>
          <p>
            The standout feature is the custom WebGL background using Perlin noise to generate organic wave patterns
            with a retro dithering effect. The shader implements:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Fractal Brownian Motion (FBM) for natural-looking waves</li>
            <li>Bayer matrix 8x8 dithering for retro aesthetic</li>
            <li>Mouse interaction with smooth damping</li>
            <li>Fade-in animation on page load</li>
            <li>Responsive canvas resizing</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Performance Considerations</h2>
          <p>
            The site is built with performance in mind:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Zero-JS-by-default with Astro</li>
            <li>Selective hydration for interactive components</li>
            <li>Static HTML generation for fast initial loads</li>
            <li>Font preloading and optimization</li>
            <li>Efficient WebGL rendering at 60fps</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Development Process</h2>
          <p>
            Built collaboratively with Claude Code, this project showcases modern web development practices
            including component-based architecture, type safety, and performance optimization. The codebase
            is organized, well-documented, and follows best practices for maintainability.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Future Enhancements</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Additional project showcase pages</li>
            <li>Blog content and writing</li>
            <li>Dark/light mode toggle</li>
            <li>More interactive WebGL effects</li>
            <li>Portfolio case studies</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .project-detail-page {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
    }

    .hero-bg {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-bg .dither-container {
      pointer-events: auto;
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .hero-bg.no-fade .dither-container {
      animation: none;
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .top-menu {
      position: fixed;
      top: 2rem;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 10;
      display: flex;
      gap: 5rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.123);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);
      border-radius: 999px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .top-menu a {
      color: #e5e7eb;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .top-menu a:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .project-container {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .back-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
      border-radius: 999px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      transform: translateX(-4px);
    }

    .project-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .project-meta {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
      border-radius: 12px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    }

    .tech-tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .tech-tag {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .external-link {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 999px;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .external-link:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .project-content {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 3rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    }

    .content-section {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .content-section:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .content-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .content-section p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .content-section ul {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      line-height: 1.8;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .content-section li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .project-detail-page {
        padding: 6rem 1rem 2rem;
      }

      .project-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .project-content {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .top-menu {
        gap: 2rem;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      }

      .top-menu a {
        padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
